message.body: My mom's getting in late today so I'm going to make potato soup for us. Wish me luck!

Hey baby. I made the soup without incidence! I want to wait to eat it with you though since no one else is going to eat it for dinner. Do you know if you'll get out on time- ish? If not, I'll eat it now. Haha.
Sorry. I was just gonna text you
Well I'm gonna take that as meaning you are still at work so I am eating.
Yeah I was going to text saying I'm still at work and to eat but then someone came to see me about a problem
